## 🔗 Dependencies

| Class | Why It's Needed |
|---|---|
| `models.Challenge` | The core object this service manages |
| `models.Company` | Challenge creation is delegated to the Company |
| `models.Evaluator` | Used in `assignEvaluator()` to validate and link |

`ChallengeService` does **not** depend on `User` directly — it works with concrete subclasses (`Company`, `Evaluator`) only where necessary.

